node.title: Queen Elizabeth backs plan to one day call Prince Charles' wife Queen Camilla
node.alt: Queen Elizabeth accepts a flower from a little girl at her Platinum Jubilee celebrations, England, February 5, 2022.
node.description: Queen Elizabeth II offers her support to have the Duchess of Cornwall become Queen Camilla
node.content: ["Queen Elizabeth II offered her support on Saturday for\u00a0the Duchess of Cornwall to become Queen Camilla.", "She used\u00a0a special Platinum Jubilee message to make public her\u00a0significant decision that will help\u00a0shape\u00a0the future of the British monarchy.", "More to come.\u00a0"]
